</P>
<P>
 "From our perspective, we're just continuing to work," she said. She vowed to 
fight on through legal means as a team of 16 investigators she hired began 
looking into complaints of voter fraud and election irregularities. 
</P>
<P>
 During the day, Sauerbrey closed to within 1,569 votes of Glendening after 
