<P>
 St. Bernard 7, St. Francis 6 -- Andrew Dillard intercepted a John Carnevali 
pass with 2:37 left and preserved a Viking victory at St. Francis. 
</P>
<P>
 St. Bernard (5-5, 2-3) took a 7-0 lead in the fourth quarter when Dillard (70 
yards in 16 carries) scored on a two-yard run. 
</P>
<P>
