<P>
 Arcadia 21, Crescenta Valley 14 -- Jon Shepherd helped host Arcadia (8-2, 3-2) 
clinch a playoff berth when he intercepted a pass on the Arcadia 37-yard line 
with 1:31 to play to preserve the victory. Shepherd also rushed for 189 yards 
and one touchdown in 32 carries. 
</P>
<P>
