pass by Wagner and ran 57 yards for a touchdown. After Arcadia was forced to 
punt on its ensuing possession, Jon Watts hit Jose Escalero with a 25-yard 
touchdown pass play to cut the deficit to 21-14 at halftime. 
</P>
