Bosco 20, and the Indians capitalized with a 28-yard touchdown pass from 
Arguella to B.C. Andreasen. 
</P>
<P>
 Two plays later, linebacker Steve Hill recovered a fumble at the St. John 
Bosco 37 that set up a one-yard touchdown run by running back Gus Lopez. 
</P>
<P>
 Arguella completed eight of 17 for 141 yards for Alemany, but was sacked six 
times. PETER YOON 
