day Who's Doing It 
</P>
<P>
 Weather is a major factor in the fluctuation of skier visits in the Pacific 
area, which includes Alaska, Arizona, California, Nevada, Oregon and 
Washington. For example, 1991 was a poor year for snow compared to 1989. 
</P>
