<HEADLINE>
<P>
COUNTYWIDE FOCUS: MOTOR OIL RECYCLING INCREASES IN COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MATTHEW MOSK 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The list of Ventura County stores willing to buy used motor oil for recycling 
has tripled this year, as the state-sponsored push to reduce waste and prevent 
illegal dumping has taken off, state officials said. 
</P>
<P>
 The decisions by several major companies to begin purchasing recycled oil 
products have contributed to a jump in statewide sales, from 6,000 gallons in 
January to more than 50,000 gallons in October, according to the California 
Integrated Waste Management Board. 
</P>
<P>
 Since the program to reclaim used oil began in April, 1993, Ventura County 
residents have recycled 74,000 gallons. And in the past six months, officials 
said, county stores participating in the buy-back program jumped from six to 
21. 
</P>
<P>
 "We're asking people to sell back their oil to prevent them from dumping it 
illegally," said Liza Smith, a management board spokeswoman. "In addition, it 
helps save our valuable oil resources." 
</P>
<P>
 Stores acting as oil collection centers will pay 16 cents per gallon of used 
oil, a management board official said. 
</P>
<P>
 Those centers in Ventura County are Adamson Auto Repair, 214 S. Bryant St., 
Ojai; Chief Auto Parts, 2375 Sycamore Drive, Simi Valley, and 150 W. Laurel 
St., Oxnard; Dowler's Tune-Up & Smog, 820 E. 5th St., Oxnard, and Easy Oil, 77 
Park Lane, Unit F, Moorpark. 
</P>
<P>
 More are Gabriels Independent Auto Repair, 65 W. Baldwin Road, Ojai; Jiffy 
Lube, 2905 Thousand Oaks Blvd., Thousand Oaks, 274 Arneill Road, Camarillo, and 
1098 E. Thompson Blvd., Ventura; Lube Pit Stop, 2170 1st St., and 4560 Los 
Angeles Ave., both in Simi Valley, and Ojai Valley Imports, 996 E. Ojai Ave., 
Ojai. 
</P>
<P>
 Others include Parnelli Jones Inc. locations at 2787 Daily Drive, Camarillo; 
355 Ventura St., Fillmore; 108 E. Harvard Blvd., Santa Paula; 955 S. A St., 
Oxnard, and 918 E. Thompson Blvd., Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Also Pep Boys, 2099 E. Thousand Oaks Blvd., Thousand Oaks; Poole Oil Co., 3885 
Vineyard Ave., Oxnard; Tune-Ups Plus, 801 E. Main St., Santa Paula, and Ventura 
Oil Co., 3815 Vineyard Ave., Oxnard. MATTHEW MOSK 
</P>
</TEXT>
