<DOCNO> LA111294-0212 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 097933 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 12, 1994, Saturday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 12; Column 4; Metro Desk 
