water polo tournament Friday at Long Beach. 
</P>
<P>
 It was the fourth consecutive victory for UC Irvine (9-11), the ninth-ranked 
team in the nation. 
</P>
<P>
 The Anteaters play California at 11 today at Long Beach Belmont Plaza. 
</P>
<P>
 In the Rolex ITA Southern California Regionals: 
</P>
<P>
 Top players advance -- Top-seeded Keri Phebus (UCLA) and No. 2 Jane Chi (UCLA) 
advanced to the quarterfinals in play at UC Irvine. 
</P>
<P>
 Phebus, from Corona del Mar High, also teamed with Susie Starrett to beat 
Arizona State's Stephanie Landsdorp and Reka Cseresnyes, 6-2, 6-1, to advance 
in doubles. 
</P>
