 In nonconference men's swimming and diving: 
</P>
<P>
 UC Irvine 63, New Mexico State 46; Northern Arizona 68, UC Irvine 41 -- Pat 
Keenan won the 200 butterfly (2:00.12) and 200 freestyle (1:46.65) and Jeff 
Hoskinson won the 200 backstroke (2:02.85) and 200 individual medley (2:03.50) 
for UC Irvine. 
</P>
