Rowe and Shelly Wright set a pool record, winning the 400-medley relay in 
4:03.14 for UC Irvine. 
</P>
<P>
 In Big West Conference women's volleyball: 
</P>
<P>
 Long Beach State 3, San Jose State 1 -- Nichelle Burton had 17 kills and Traci 
Dahl added 13 kills to lead visiting Long Beach State, 8-15, 15-5, 15-3, 15-6. 
</P>
<P>
 Utah State 3, Cal State Fullerton 2 -- Lisi Fa'agata had 18 kills and Jennifer 
Lipski added 13 for Cal State Fullerton, which lost, 9-15, 15-8, 14-16, 15-12, 
15-9. 
