Grayeli added five to lead Costa Mesa (23-5) in the blowout. Costa Mesa will 
play Marina in a quarterfinals Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Los Alamitos 12, El Dorado 7 -- Eric Ploessel scored five goals, Tim Campbell 
