<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Welfare Benefits -- Because of an editing error, a story in Friday's editions 
misstated plans by congressional Republicans to change eligibility for welfare 
benefits. The story said that illegal immigrants would be denied assistance. 
Illegal immigrants are already ineligible; the Republican plan would end 
benefits for legal immigrants. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
